gomodel:SYNGO_2445  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.2: \"Ultrastructural localization of PNP 14 immunoreactivity in the rat cerebellar cortex\"\n- Literal: \"Electron microscopic observation revealed many gold particles representing PNP 14 immunoreactivity, in axon terminals.. In addition, the gold particles indicating PNP 14 immunoreactivities were observed throughout the cytoplasmic matrices in the axon terminals. However, few gold particles were detected on the mitochondria, small clear synaptic vesicles and dense granular vesicles in the axon terminals.\". Experimental description: \"Ultrastructural localization of PNP 14 immunoreactivity in the rat cerebellar cortex\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0755-5899" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-7351-8706" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3185-5709" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0938-8534" ;
        dc:date           "2018-02-09" ;
